-- N.Y. Gallery Owner to Plead Guilty to Role in Gambling Ring
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2013-11-12T19:40:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-12/n-y-gallery-owner-to-plead-guilty-to-role-in-gambling-ring.html
Manhattan  art gallery owner Hillel
“Helly” Nahmad will plead guilty to one count of operating an
illegal gambling ring that catered to celebrities and the very
wealthy, the U.S. said in a letter to a judge in Manhattan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
